OL,5,CSWAMPY ARRESTED AT RUNWAY DEMO         
OL,7,GRoads protester Swampy was arrested by 
OL,8,Gpolice during action to halt Manchester
OL,9,GAirport's #170m second runway.         
OL,10,G                                       
OL,11,GThe activist, real name Daniel Hooper, 
OL,12,Gwas arrested on suspicion of criminal  
OL,13,Gdamage to a perimeter fence.           
OL,14,F                                       
OL,15,GThe 23-year-old from Hazlemere, Bucks, 
OL,16,Gbecame a household name when he was the
OL,17,Glast to emerge from the 30ft tunnels   
OL,18,Gdug by protesters to Devon's A30 bypass
