OL,5,CEX-MINISTER IN U-TURN ON ROADS         
OL,7,GFormer Tory transport minister Steven  
OL,8, Norris has given his backing to anti-  
OL,9, roads protesters and admits the        
OL,10, countryside disrupted by the Newbury   
OL,11, bypass could have been left alone.     
OL,12,G                                       
OL,13,GIn an outspoken U-turn on Government   
OL,14,Gpolicy Mr Norris says he believes it is
OL,15, wrong to "pander" to traffic growth for
OL,16, the sake of "frustrated motorists".    
OL,17,F                                       
OL,18,GHis comments come in a BBC Panorama    
OL,19, traffic inquiry to be broadcast tonight
