OL,5,CFOX-HUNTERS THREATEN RIOTS             
OL,7,GThe hunting lobby says there would be a
OL,8, "riot in the countryside" if a Labour  
OL,9, government abolished fox-hunting.      
OL,11, Hunting groups say anger among their   
OL,12, supporters over Labour's proposals have
OL,13,Gbecome so intense it would be          
OL,14, impossible to prevent their resorting  
OL,15, to "civil disobedience".               
OL,17, A spokesman from the British Field     
OL,18, Sports Society says: "We have to show  
OL,19, that we won't be messed about with!"   
