OL,5,CISLAND SANCTUARY FOR OTTERS            
OL,7,GThe former island home of Gavin        
OL,8, Maxwell, author of Ring of Bright      
OL,9, Water, is to be made into a wildlife   
OL,10, sanctuary for otters.                  
OL,12, Eilean Ban, a six-acre isle between    
OL,13, mainland Scotland and Skye, is to be   
OL,14, handed over to a trust run by the local
OL,15, community, 30 years after his death.   
OL,17, A spokesman from the Scottish Office   
OL,18, says: "It will be of environmental     
OL,19, benefit to the people of Skye."        
