OL,5,CBRITISH SHIP IN NUCLEAR WASTE ROW      
OL,7, A British ship carrying nuclear waste  
OL,8, is at the centre of a big demonstration
OL,9, in northern Japan, a week after the    
OL,10, country's worst nuclear accident.      
OL,12, The Pacific Teal is scheduled to       
OL,13, arrive tomorrow at Mutsu-Ogawara in    
OL,14, Aomori Prefecture, about 360 miles     
OL,15, north-east of Tokyo.                   
OL,17, Greenpeace Japan say they plan rallies 
OL,18, early tomorrow morning in the quiet    
OL,19, Japanese port.                         
